section.section:
Subject to paragraph (3) of this subsection, the Commission may cooperate with and enter into agreements to obtain and provide insurance coverage in the most economical manner with:
Montgomery County;
Prince George's County;
both Montgomery County and Prince George's County; or
subject to the approval of the county government of a county affected by the agreement, other units of government.

An agreement under paragraph (1) of this subsection may provide for any type of insurance protection, including:
public liability;
group health, life, hospitalization, and disability;
real and personal property; and
workers' compensation.
